    <p>• Thai po­lice yes­ter­day de­tained two ac­tivists in the first ar­rests against an in­creas­ingly bold move­ment of young pro­test­ers call­ing for democ­racy and chal­leng­ing a con­tro­ver­sial law that pro­tects the monar­chy.</p>
    <p>In re­cent weeks, near daily ral­lies have been held at univer­si­ties and town halls across the coun­try to de­nounce the mil­i­tary-aligned gov­ern­ment of Prime Min­is­ter Prayut Chan-o-cha.</p>


